This test will check klettres accepts the correctly entered letters
<dl>
    <dt>Launch klettres</dt>
        <dd>klettres opens, showing one alphabet by default on the screen</dd>
    <dt>Enter the alphabet correctly in the textbox</dt>
        <dd>The application accepts the letter and shows another letter</dd>
</dl>

This test will check klettres does not accept the incorrect letters
<dl>
    <dt>Enter an incorrect letter in the textbox</dt>
        <dd>The application does not accept the letter and shows the existing letter</dd>
</dl>

